<div type="Stephanus-page" n="5">
<div type="section" n="c">
<l n="1"><label type="speaker" rend="indent(1)">ΣΩ.</label> πρῶτον μὲν λόγος </l>
<l n="2">δεύτερος καὶ τρί-</l>
</div>
<div type="section" n="e">
<l n="1">τος ἔστω. <label type="speaker">ΕΥΘ.</label> καλῶς λέγεις <pb/> </l>
<l n="2">καὶ πάλιν αὖθις πε-</l>
</div>
</div>
<div type="Stephanus-page" n="6">
<div type="section" n="a">
<l n="1">ραίνω ταῦτα τὰ αὐτά. </l>
<l n="2"><label type="speaker" rend="indent(1)">ΣΩ.</label> τέλος. </l>
</div>
</div>
